Package: crssplot
Title: Create Standard CRSS Plots
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alan",
           family = "Butler",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "rabutler@usbr.gov",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Creates the 'standard' set of CRSS figures that are used to 
    review model runs. User input is provided via yml files to make it quick
    and easy to make multiple comparisons from many different scenarios. 
